<h2 style="margin:0 0 10px 0; font-size:22px; font-weight:600;">
    Application Termination Approved
</h2>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:25px 0;">
    Hello {{homeBuyerName}},
</p>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    Your request to terminate your mortgage application has been approved. Please review the details below.
</p>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    <strong>Termination Details:</strong>
</p>

<table style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0; border-collapse:collapse;">
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Application Number:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;"><strong>{{applicationNumber}}</strong></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Property:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;">{{propertyName}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Termination Date:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;">{{terminationDate}}</td>
    </tr>
</table>

{{#if refundAmount}}
<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:15px 0;">
    <strong>Refund Information:</strong>
</p>

<table style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0; border-collapse:collapse;">
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Total Paid:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;">{{totalPaid}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Refund Amount:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;"><strong>{{refundAmount}}</strong></td>
    </tr>
    {{#if deductions}}
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Deductions:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;">{{deductions}}</td>
    </tr>
    {{/if}}
</table>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    Your refund will be processed within 7-14 business days to your original payment method.
</p>
{{/if}}

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    We're sorry to see you go. If your circumstances change in the future, we'd be happy to assist you on your homeownership journey.
</p>

<a href="{{dashboardLink}}"
    style="color:#ffffff; padding:8px 20px; text-decoration:none; font-size:14px; font-family:Arial, sans-serif; border-radius:12px; display:inline-block; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #049DC8 0%, #0082B5 100%); border: none; margin-top:15px;">
    View Details
</a>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:20px; margin-top:30px;">
    Best, <br />
    The {{projectName}} Team.
</p>
